; Auto-generated placeholder for Ashurim.
; Drop real environment art under MeshRoot; lighting/atmosphere already tuned.
; Atmosphere: First town. Where the six paths converge after class intros. The Storyteller waits at the well; Iddinu mans the smithy; pilgrims drink in the chapel courtyard. Safe zone.
; Palette: Hearth-orange · timber-brown · cream stone
; Level range: 5-7

